      "section": "0 \u00b7 Executive Summary",
      "subsections": [
        {
          "title": "0.1 Overview",
          "content": "This Stage 4.3 Business Requirements (BR) converts approved PRD features (Stage 4.1) and User Stories (Stage 4.2) for the Lightweight Self Hosted CRM into measurable commitments with SMART KPIs, acceptance metrics, compliance tags, and sprint bundling. The BR focuses on cost reduction versus Dynamics 365, fast and reliable CRUD, secure RBAC with full audit, deterministic ID issuance, operational durability via backup/restore, accurate dashboards, and a reproducible Docker/Replit deployment."
        },
        {
          "title": "0.2 Objectives & Non\u2011Negotiables",
          "rows": [
            {
              "objective": "Reduce CRM software costs vs current Dynamics plan",
              "target": "\u2265 60% savings",
              "source": "Stage 1 Success Metrics"
            },
            {
              "objective": "Performance",
              "target": "Median page response \u2264 2s; P95 API reads \u2264 500ms",
              "source": "Stage 1 / PRD"
            },
            {
              "objective": "Security",
              "target": "Deny\u2011by\u2011default RBAC with 100% protected route coverage",
              "source": "Stage 1 / PRD"
            },
            {
              "objective": "Resilience",
              "target": "Backup \u2264 5 min and Restore \u2264 15 min for \u2264 2 GB",
              "source": "Stage 1"
            },
            {
              "objective": "Adoption",
              "target": "\u2265 5 active users in first month",
              "source": "Stage 1"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
